---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Gracias por contactarnos - Mafra Logistics">

  <section class="relative bg-gray-900 min-h-[60vh] flex items-center">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 overflow-hidden">
      <img src="/hero-mafra.jpg" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-45" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary/90 via-secondary/60 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 w-full py-16 flex flex-col items-center text-center text-white">
      <div class="bg-primary/20 border border-primary/40 rounded-full p-4 mb-6">
        <i class="ph ph-check-circle text-5xl text-primary"></i>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-tight">¡Gracias por contactarnos!</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-200 max-w-xl">Recibimos tu solicitud correctamente. Uno de nuestros asesores se pondrá en contacto contigo a la brevedad para cotizar tu flete.</p>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/" class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded text-sm transition-colors shadow-sm inline-flex items-center gap-2">
          <i class="ph ph-arrow-left text-lg"></i>
          Volver al Inicio
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+528129115812" class="bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 border border-white/30 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded text-sm transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2">
          <i class="ph ph-phone-call text-lg"></i>
          Cotizar Ahora
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
